OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill see scattered showers. Showers
OL,7,Fgradually dying out through the early
OL,8,Fhours, becoming dry by dawn. A cold
OL,9,Fnight with frost in sheltered glens.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,12,Fsunshine. Dry and cloudier in the
OL,13,Fafternoon, patchy rain spreading
OL,14,Fnortheast in the evening along with
OL,15,Fstrengthening southeasterly winds.
OL,16,FRather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
