OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain clearing away on
OL,7,FSaturday morning then mainly dry and
OL,8,Fbright with occasional showers. More
OL,9,Fin the way of showers on Sunday and
OL,10,FMonday.
